bitcoin-all-key-generator
=========================

###### directory.io without the latency

##### [Install Go](http://golang.org/doc/install)

##### Install dependencies:
```bash
$ go get github.com/btcsuite/btcutil
```

##### Run:
```bash
$ go run generate.go
```
